725100f-a.title: Queens: 20th Road - 36th Street
725100f-a.text:
20th Road (01d Bowery Bay Road; right), west from 36th Street, (not shown
showing at the left the Lawrence family burial place at the S.E. corner
of 35th Street and 20th Road. The houses at the left are on the west
side of 35th Street.
May 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
